data.title: Networker Gallery "Nenad Bogdanovic." by Bogdanovic, Nenad.: (1996) Signed by Author(s) Art / Print / Poster
data.meta_description: Signed by Author(s) - Torino: Maurizio Spatola. - 1996 - Condition: Good - One visual poem on thin ecru paper, measuring 21 x 30 cm, signed and numbered 78/300 in ink by the artist. Item is an "object-leaf" from Geiger 10 per Adriano Spatola, an anthology of experimental art and concrete and visual poetry published in memory of Adriano Spatola and edited by Maurizio Spatola in collaboration with Arrigo Lora-Totino and Franco Beltrametti. - Networker Gallery "Nenad Bogdanovic."
